Expected Result: The "Add Reason" button is marked as invalid after:  - the user changes focus from the stock on hand field, and the values don't match,  - the user has an unaccounted values after editing in the modal (more later),  - the user attempts to submit the form when there is still a difference  - If the user has entered a single reason, the reason is shown in the button,  - if the user has more than one reason, the button reads "<n> Reasons" (where n is the number of reasons) and - - When this button is hovered or focused, a popover is shown that lists the reasons and their amounts
